{"tid":883291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南極罕見爆發謀殺案　科學家被「劇透」怒砍同事","createTime":"2018-10-30T17:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T07:53:56.000Z","uid":34572,"like":834,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"3d1feccee096a83b55954aa7a352a6e0de89c41b","tid":883291,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:16:28.000Z","msg":"南極罕見謀殺案！在南極洲偏遠基地工作的科學家謝爾蓋（Sergey Savitsky），日前用菜刀攻擊同事奧列格（Oleg Beloguzov），使得奧列格心臟受損仍在重症看護中，而謝爾蓋行兇的原因，竟然是自己閱讀書籍被對方「劇透」揭露結局。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，謝爾蓋在南極洲的研究工作相當艱苦，只能依靠閱讀來娛樂，然而奧列格不斷地透露書籍中之後的情節，使得謝爾蓋相當憤怒才會行兇。目前謝爾蓋因涉嫌謀殺未遂，被拘留在俄羅斯聖彼得堡。報導中指出，這應該是南極洲首次有人被控謀殺。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"00c0cdf81bfd02fc24fe3b51a866ae4696563aaa","tid":883291,"uid":214036,"like":808,"dislike":4,"score":804,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:18:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e252fbbac4b8611a793993239384c7c2e20700c","tid":883291,"uid":166785,"like":261,"dislike":0,"score":261,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:20:07.000Z","msg":"我都唔知講咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5bca7dd6d45c96e1ec92ed0d88ce193b316263","tid":883291,"uid":83060,"like":101,"dislike":3,"score":98,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:20:23.000Z","msg":"南極警方拉人未"},{"pid":"a02a7969b41fae4f11bdb32476f71c38cab221b3","tid":883291,"uid":69083,"like":746,"dislike":3,"score":743,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:21:22.000Z","msg":"劇透死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc980a96f8071a9fb2dff23c8b606db441a75a3","tid":883291,"uid":146340,"like":907,"dislike":3,"score":904,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:21:59.000Z","msg":"抵啦 已經想像到條友係南極嬉皮笑臉劇透個仆街樣"},{"pid":"f00c888fee2b0389f8169b3e7017b4037c866707","tid":883291,"uid":2419,"like":324,"dislike":2,"score":322,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:22:44.000Z","msg":"劇透不嬲都死全家架啦 而家便宜左佢仲想點"},{"p